message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper discusses the use of deep learning for medical image processing, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper specifically focuses on the healthcare sector (cs.MED) and discusses the challenges and future directions for deep learning in this field, which could also fall under the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NEURON) sub-category.
